strings: <se_low>jungmi: This road leads directly to our house.
<se_low>jungmi: Before you leave, you need to find out what happened in the shelter. I need to talk to you!
<voice_0x0100177F><se_low>*: Send now! what are you doing here
<voice_0x01001780><se_low>*: Eh...! If you have the power to become a dragon, I'll burn you to death on the spot!
<voice_0x01001781><se_low>jungmi: I hope my declining health doesn't make up for the hatred towards others.
<voice_0x01001782><se_low>*: You. Chen Mi, that's how you brought these people to our refuge!
<voice_0x01001783><se_low>*: Meaning<:> Outlaw! Crazy idea, your daughter entrusted us humans!
<voice_0x01001784><se_low>jungmi: Is this an insult to our race? Has not changed.
<voice_0x01001785><se_low>jungmi: There's no reason to argue over a rock. Let go of that stubborn old man.
<voice_0x01001786><se_low>jungmi: Stupid or not, catching a man in bed is never a good idea.
